2022-01-19 19:19:13	bn_mobile	Hi, I have a force diagram question.  If a foot with a oblique spiral fracture of the 5th metatarsal occurs, how would that alter the distribution of forces in the foot (say with 85lbs of weight/force vector from the proximal (top) direction of the foot)?
